  "title": "Part Timer Cleaner 兼职清洁工 (Up to 高达$20/hour)",
  "description": "<p>Job Description工作</p><ul><li>Perform general cleaning duties in office spaces, workshop areas, pantry, toilets and other designated spaces. 在办公室、工作区、茶水间、厕所和其他场域的常规清理工作。</li><li>Empty trash bins as needed. 清理垃圾。</li><li>Monitor and replenish cleaning supplies as necessary. 确保清理用具不短缺。</li><li>Adhere to a regular cleaning schedule as outlined by the supervisor. 根据主管的指示进行其他的定期清理工作。</li><li>Working hour: Mon & Wed & Fri, 5 hours per day。工作时间：星期一&三&五，一天五个小时。</li><li>Salary is CPF-able. 薪水会支付CPF。</li></ul>",
